harddisk I/O error
dev 0303, block 0
Unable to read partition table of device 303
[but the extended drive within hda3 was recognized already with exact size!]
part 4 [ .... start size end stuff]
Partition tables ok
Kernel panic. Unable to mount root [Why that ??? Root is 304!]

